---
layout: department.njk
title: City Clerk
subtitle: Official city records, meeting agendas and minutes, elections, and public information requests.
description: Aberdeen City Clerk — meeting agendas, council minutes, elections, MPIA requests, and official city records. Call (410) 272-1600 ext. 211.
deptPhone: "(410) 272-1600 ext. 211"
deptRealUrl: "https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/city-clerk"
---

<div class="space-y-10">
  <div>
    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">The City Clerk serves as the official keeper of City records, manages City Council meeting logistics including agendas and minutes, administers municipal elections, and processes Maryland Public Information Act requests.</p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-5">Services</h2>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      {% for service in [
        { title: "Meeting Agendas & Minutes", desc: "All Council and board meeting documents, past and present." },
        { title: "Live Meeting Stream", desc: "Watch City Council meetings live online." },
        { title: "Municipal Elections", desc: "Voter registration, candidate packets, and election results." },
        { title: "Public Records (MPIA)", desc: "Maryland Public Information Act request processing." },
        { title: "Proclamation Requests", desc: "Requests for City proclamations and official recognitions." },
        { title: "City Charter & Code", desc: "Official City of Aberdeen Charter and Code of Ordinances." }
      ] %}
      <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-navy mb-1">{{ service.title }}</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-600">{{ service.desc }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-5">Upcoming Meetings</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-3">
      {% for meeting in events.meetings %}
      <li>
        <a href="{{ meeting.url }}" class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:border-gov-blue hover:shadow-sm transition-all duration-200 group">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-navy text-white rounded-lg flex flex-col items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-center leading-none">
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold opacity-70 uppercase">{{ meeting.month }}</span>
            <span class="text-lg font-bold">{{ meeting.day }}</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-bold text-navy group-hover:text-gov-blue transition-colors duration-200">{{ meeting.title }}</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5">{{ meeting.location }}</div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-5">Quick Links</h2>
    <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
      {% for link in [
        { label: "Meetings & Agendas", url: "/services/meetings/" },
        { label: "Public Records Request", url: "/services/public-records/" },
        { label: "Elections", url: "/services/elections/" },
        { label: "Council Minutes Archive", url: "https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/node/2090/minutes" },
        { label: "Frequently Requested Docs", url: "https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/city-clerk/pages/meetings" },
        { label: "Watch Live Meetings", url: "https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/city-clerk/pages/meetings" }
      ] %}
      <a href="{{ link.url | url }}" class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 text-sm text-slate-700 font-medium px-5 py-3 hover:text-gov-blue hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors duration-150 group border-b border-slate-100 last:border-b-0">
        {{ link.label }}
        <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400 group-hover:text-gov-blue flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
